The paper proposes and evaluates methods for strengthening proof automation by learning from proof libraries of different provers. This involves the use of machine learning and reasoning systems, which are commonly associated with the sub-categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI), logic in computer science (cs.LO), programming languages (cs.PL), software engineering (cs.SE), and machine learning (cs.LG).
